Package org.horrabin.horrorss

Interface Summary
RssModuleParser Implement this interface if you want to obtain elements from the RSS file that are not parsed by default
 

Class Summary
RssChannelBean The RssChannelBean object maps the element channel of an RSS feed.
RssFeed The RssFeed class maps the elements of an RSS feed (channel, image and a list of items)
RssImageBean The RssImageBean object maps the element image of an RSS feed.
RssItemBean The RssItemBean object maps the element item of an RSS feed.
RssParser RSS file parser compatible with all RSS, RDF & Atom specifications.
